social_posts.post_text:
It’s always a great idea to get off of the resort and explore your destination!
Our family did an incredible private tour with Living Dreams Excursions where we snorkelled with sea turtles and sting rays, ziplined into cenotes, saw wild monkeys in the jungle, had a delicious lunch in a Mayan village as well as hot, fresh churros and we made all of the memories!

Making memories while we travel with our family is one of my favourite things to do♥️
#mexico2022

I don’t know about you but one of the best things about vacations is NOT COOKING or doing the dishes, or thinking about what to make for supper! What a treat! 
Have you booked your break from the kitchen yet?!

Atelier Playa Mujeres - my favourite adults only resort in Playa Mujeres♥️
Contact me to book your escape from the cold!

#travel #travellife #explore #world #makingmemories #atelierplayamujeres #vacation #family #adultsonlytravel #mexico #ilovemexico #travelgram #travelphotography #travelling #traveling #travelblogger #traveldiaries #traveladdict #instatravel #adventure #traveltheworld  #beachbabe #wanderlust #goexplore #beachbum #seekmoments #trip #magicalmexico

Some pretty great clients of mine departed today for a week in Mexico at the gorgeous Dreams Natura resort …. I know they will love it as much as our family did!
I can’t wait to see all the pics!
Nothing says “open your eyes and live your life!” than a helicopter tour over West Maui and Molokai - one of the best travel experiences of my life! @airmaui

I absolutely love PV, Mexico!!
I booked a family vaycay to Puerto Vallarta … I’m so excited to take my younger three girls to a destination they have never been! 🌴✈️💃🏼

There’s just something about waking up in paradise and seeing the ocean for the first time♥️🌴🌊 
I was so pleased that we were able to make this trip happen for this lovely family!

Maui - where my heart feels at home. 
It’s been almost 3 years since I’ve been able to visit this glorious island and I can’t wait to go back!🌴

No bad days in Mazatlan!🌴🐳
Sand and sun all day long!☀️
There’s nothing like a family vacation to Mexico ♥️🌴✈️
Amazing week in Mazatlan with my family ♥️

Whenever we explore a new destination I like to do one water adventure and one land excursion! 
In Mazatlan, we rented a private boat for the morning to cruise around the islands of Mazatlan, to watch whales and sea lions! 
It was so nice to get out on the water and take in that ocean breeze! 🌊🐳🦭

Not a bad morning spot to sip some coffee and enjoy the ocean views from our swim out suite ☀️🌴☕️ 
This is the Elegance Club Swim Up Suite with Outdoor Jacuzzi at the Majestic Elegance Costa Mujeres. A gorgeous suite with a living area, king bed and one and half bathrooms. This room also comes with a butler, one bottle of alcohol of your choosing, 24 hour room service and so much more!

Today we spent the afternoon at the gorgeous spa! We did the hydrotherapy circuit and had a facial and massage - it was so relaxing!
I definitely think that everyone should experience the spa at least once on vacation… life is too short not to pamper yourself a little bit!
After our spa treatments we had a delicious late lunch by the ocean! #lovingeveryminute

social_posts.post_text:
Waking up in paradise never gets old!
I caught the sunrise this morning and it was amazing! 🌴☀️🌊
Time is non-refundable, spend it wisely🌴☀️

The Grand Palladium Costa Mujeres and the TRS Coral (adults only section) are two stunning resorts that I checked out while I was in Costa Mujeres. Amazing for families and couples alike with beautiful, lush grounds and a stunning beach!
No regrets ✌🏼

A dose of vitamin D ☀️ and some sibling rivalry ✌🏼
This was almost 4 years ago - cherish these memories because they really do go by too fast🥹🌴
Nobody’s missing school this week ✌🏼🌴🍹
Beautiful beach day at Destiladeras beach with friends! Nothing beats buying fresh fruit and candy from the beach vendors to snack on while you’re catching some rays! ☀️ 🌊🌴

Lots of families are securing their vacation plans for next winter and now is truly the best time to do so while there is still availability (some flights are already sold out😳🫣)
Travelling with my family is my favourite- always has been, always will be!♥️✈️

Good Morning & Happy Thursday! 💃

I will be away from my office from August 7-12 on a familiarization trip to Cancun with Karisma Resorts!
I will have very limited access to my emails while I am there as I am doing site inspections at all Karisma resorts in the destination. 
I will be staying at the brand new Adults Only Margaritaville Island Reserve Riviera Maya!

These are the resorts I will be seeing:

Margaritaville Island Reserve Riviera Maya, by Karisma
Nickelodeon Hotels & Resorts Riviera Maya, by Karisma & Aqua Nick Water Park
Margaritaville Island Reserve Riviera Cancun, by Karisma
Azul Beach Resort Riviera Cancun, by Karisma
El Dorado Maroma
Palafitos-Overwater Bungalows 
El Dorado Seaside Suites
El Dorado Seaside Palms 
El Dorado Royale, El Dorado Casitas Royale
Generations Riviera Maya

If you are wanting to book a vacation, please reach out to me before I leave or contact Jada Martens (@jadamartens_tpi ) or email jmartens@tpi.ca while I am away!

Stay tuned for updates! 🌴✈️
Thrilled to spend the next 4 nights at the gorgeous, brand new, adults only Margaritaville Riviera Maya … I’m digging the turquoise colours and beach decor, it’s right up my alley! 🌊🏄‍♀️🦜🍹

Best way to start the day in Margaritaville! 

#MargaritavilleIslandReserve 
#KarismaExperience #GourmetInclusive

I’ve been to the stunning El Dorado Maroma before but I was reminded to how romantic and serene this resort is. Perfect to celebrate an anniversary or get away for your honeymoon!

Located at Maroma Beach, one of the top beaches in Mexico, El Dorado Maroma is the perfect place to lay back and relax. 

#ExperienceElDorado
#KarismaExperience #GourmetInclusive 
#adultsonlyresort.

It ́s five o ́clock somewhere! Enjoy the first all-inclusive Margaritaville Island Reserve Resort with activities that will keep you engaged and relaxed during your visit. Fins Up!

Margaritaville Riviera Cancun is a family resort (but it’s not one that is ALL ABOUT KIDS like the Nickelodeon). They do have a kids club and toddler amenities per request in the rooms. 
It’s a super chill vibe with a focus on gourmet dining and music!🌴🦜🎶 
#KarismaExperience #GourmetInclusive

The perfect way to describe a multigenerational resort is Azul Beach Resort Riviera Cancun, by Karisma. Featuring an Adults Section with its own pool, swim up bar and entertainment and a family section that offers guaranteed connecting suites! 

I’ve sold this resort a lot in the past and my clients love it - the toddler amenities are perfect for a family as they provide a crib, stroller, bottled warmer, baby monitor and so much more!

The ultimate experience in tropical bliss isn’t on the coast – it’s within the waves. El Dorado Maroma offers guests the opportunity to experience one of the Top 10 Beaches in the World in a whole new light. Palafitos-Overwater Bungalows are a cluster of 30 exclusive, private bungalows sitting right over the turquoise waters of Maroma Beach. Every single facet of these exclusive suites is designed to highlight the surrounding beauty.

Watch the sun rise and set in a stunning display of colors right from your private deck. Take a dip within your private infinity pool, offering picture-perfect views of the sparkling sea. Rinse off within your Aguas del Amor™ private outdoor shower. And let your personal Majordomo take care of the rest, as you relax in absolute bliss.

PALAFITOS-OVERWATER BUNGALOW
EXCLUSIVE FEATURES
* Full butler service
* Glass bottom floors
* Private infinity pool
* Direct ladder access to the ocean
* The romantic Aguas del Amor™ outdoor shower
* Indoor Relaxing Hot Tub for two
* Oversized deck with wooden lounge chairs
* Exclusive beach beds
* 24-hour room service
* Customized beach picnics
* Serve in-bungalow full breakfast daily
* Serve pre-dinner drinks and gourmet bites
* Liaise with housekeeping on servicing of the suite
* Dressing service before dinner

If you’re looking for a high end vacation that’ll make lifetime memories, contact me!

El Dorado Seaside Suites has breathtaking ocean views and all swim up rooms - the pool level rooms swim out into the main pool and the infinity pools are off your balcony (more of a plunge pool!). 

El Dorado Seaside Palms features 8,000+ palm trees across the property, with swings, hammocks and a beautiful beach that makes it perfect for a getaway!

These Adults Only resorts are beside each other and have exchange privileges. They are located just minutes away from the top iconic spots in the Riviera Maya and the Seaside Suites features one of the largest Spas in the destination!
The ocean in front of the Coral Level at Iberostar Selection Cancun was like none that I have ever seen. So pristine, stunning, powerful 🌊

So excited to be back at my favourite resort - the stunning adults only Atelier Playa Mujeres … this resort stole my heart the first time I was here and I can’t wait to spend the next 5 nights being pampered in paradise. 
We are staying in an Inspira Corner Suite with a plunge pool and ocean view. It’s unbelievable! 🌴

Please send my family here …
Because I’m never coming home😬
Out of Office 🍹
Never get too busy making a living that you forget to make a life♥️🌴☀️

social_posts.post_text:
Fees … let’s talk about fees! 💸

I actually don’t charge fees to my potential clients before I will send quotes or offer travel advice, and here is why - I trust you!
I trust that when you come to me as a past client, referral, or new client, that you have the best intentions of booking your vacation with me in the end - as that is how I get compensated for the time I have spent assisting you and providing options to you.
 
I have spent 12+ years researching destinations, travelling all over the world, keeping on top of travel insurance, entry requirements and the best destinations and resorts so that I can best serve my clients.  I actually care about my clients and I want you to have an amazing experience!
That is something you won’t get from booking your vacation online. 

When you take the advice I give you and book your vacation online or with another travel agent, I don’t get paid🙇🏼‍♀️. This is why most agents have started to charge fees - to show that you’re serious about booking with them and to protect their time (and I respect this!!). 
All travel agents have access to the SAME DEALS and the SAME RESORTS and the SAME FLIGHTS. When a client tells me they booked their vacation with a different agent because she posted xxx deal, I can get the same deal - all prices are regulated by the tour operators (unless the agent is selling off 1 or 2 rooms of group space they have held!). 
So if you’ve read this far, my request to you is this - please only reach out to myself or any travel agent if you plan on booking your vacation with us - don’t knowingly waste our time🙏🏼 … (changing your mind & deciding not to travel is completely different). 
Most travel agents have families, kids in sports, grandbabies to snuggle, meals that need to be made and other clients to attend to and our time is valuable & precious - just like yours is♥️
Waking up to this view … yes please!

Zoetry resorts will always have my heart - I absolutely love the Zoetry Casa Del Mar in Los Cabos! 
On our first day, we were fortunate to see lots of whales in the ocean!

The Zoetry in Cabo is sooo picturesque🌴… and most of the time it felt like we had the resort to ourselves!
If you’re looking for fine dining, great service, top shelf drinks, small & intimate (only 57 rooms!), spectacular ocean views (we even saw whales!) - the Zoetry Casa Del Mar is an excellent option!
